{"tid":906648,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"寧同中國打交道 美軍高層：科技公司做法好有問題","createTime":"2018-11-18T07:21:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-18T07:36:05.000Z","uid":28765,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fcd208ff3e2c7062334af04ce1173ac103dbb8dd","tid":906648,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T07:21:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181118/large/1542475405_0fca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181118%2Flarge%2F1542475405_0fca.jpg&h=0fbb934b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鄧福德(美聯社)<br />\n<br />\n美國參謀長聯席會議主席鄧福德(Joseph Dunford)說，美國科技巨企不想與國防部合作，但卻願意與中國打交道，這很成問題。<br />\n<br />\n鄧福德在哈利法克斯國際安全論壇上說，美國一些科技公司千方百計打入中國市場，但卻不想與美國軍方合作，令他很難過。他說：「我只有一句簡單說話：『我們是忠的』。」<br />\n<br />\n鄧福德沒有直接提及網上搜索引擎巨企Google，但數以千計Google員工年初曾聯署要求公司取消Maven計劃。該計劃是為國防部提供其人工智能運算技術，協助截取影像和改善無人機攻擊的準確性，Google其後宣佈將取消計劃。<br />\n<br />\n他說，與中國企業分享知識產權的美國科網公司，實際上是與中國軍方分享技術。他指出，二戰後美國具競爭優勢，正是因為公私營合作。<br />\n<br />\nGoogle據說正開發符合中國嚴格審查的手機版搜索引擎。鄧福德說：「這非關乎做一些不道德或違法事情，而是關於確保我們可合力維護大家支持的價值。這是我要對科技公司說的話。」<br />\n<br />\n美聯社<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181118/58926956\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181118%2F58926956&d=6tuXhv1Op5ZcMF%2FNsQcJwNZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=a5f50493\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181118%2F58926956&h=93f7160d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181118/58926956</a>"},{"pid":"747fecd9b54512daf0e0564d2f41da5db5aeaecb","tid":906648,"uid":190540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T07:33:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c76799f07719e40ceda8cd8d86cca669c17729de","tid":906648,"uid":34666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"747fecd9b54512daf0e0564d2f41da5db5aeaecb","tid":906648,"uid":190540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T07:33:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T07:36:05.000Z","msg":"果班死左仔/婆個個去開紅黃藍幼兒園<br />\n可能果度啲八月十五真係特別圓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}